Package persistency

Class testPersistency

java.lang.Object
persistency.testPersistency
public class testPersistency extends Object
This class is responsible for testing the persistancy package. When calling load or saver methods in persistancy all the methods in those classes are used. Therefore, a successful save or load shows that all of those helper methods are working.
Author:
Phillip.
